CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779718268
OL,3,CHeat to rise to possible record-
OL,4,Cbreaking highs over rest of bank
OL,5,Choliday weekend
OL,7,FSaturday also saw holidaymakers trying
OL,8,Fto get to Europe via the Port of Dover
OL,9,Fwhere they faced hours-long queues.
OL,11,FIn a bid to ease the waits, the French
OL,12,Fauthorities suspended extra EU border
OL,13,Fchecks under the new entry/exit system
OL,14,F(EES).
OL,16,FEES involves people from third-party
OL,17,Fcountries such as the UK having their
OL,18,Ffingerprints registered and a
OL,19,Fphotograph taken to enter the Schengen
OL,20,FArea, which consists of 29 European
OL,21,Fcountries, mainly in the EU.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779718268
OL,3,CHeat to rise to possible record-
OL,4,Cbreaking highs over rest of bank
OL,5,Choliday weekend
OL,7,FBy Saturday late afternoon, the port
OL,8,Fsaid the traffic was "free flowing" on
OL,9,Fits "peak day of the May half-term
OL,10,Fgetaway weekend".
OL,12,FMet Office meteorologist Jonathan
OL,13,FVautrey said there will be "plentiful
OL,14,Famounts of sunshine for the vast
OL,15,Fmajority" of people on Sunday, but it
OL,16,Flooks set to be a damp day in parts of
OL,17,Fthe North West and Scotland.
OL,26,@pD@VOUpD@cO]qD@EOUrD@PO]uD@\OUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
