OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779718268
OL,3,CHeat to rise to possible record-
OL,4,Cbreaking highs over rest of bank
OL,5,Choliday weekend
OL,7,FThe MCC, which owns Lord's, said it
OL,8,Fhas "decided to dispense with the
OL,9,Frequirement for gentlemen to wear
OL,10,Fjackets in the pavilion" for two
OL,11,FVitality Blast matches on Sunday.
OL,13,FMost will also see "wall-to-wall blue
OL,14,Fsunshine" on Monday, Mr Vautrey said.
OL,26,@pD@EOUrD@XO]uD@TOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
