OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779718268
OL,3,CHeat to rise to possible record-
OL,4,Cbreaking highs over rest of bank
OL,5,Choliday weekend
OL,7,FThe meteorologist continued: "That
OL,8,Fextra sunshine once again allowing
OL,9,Fthose temperatures to climb even
OL,10,Ffurther and so now we're expecting to
OL,11,Fsee around 33C in the far south-east
OL,12,Fof London but quite broadly a
OL,13,Fpotential for 30C into parts of
OL,14,Fnorthern England, areas of Wales and
OL,15,Fright throughout the Midlands as well.
OL,26,@oD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
