OL,3,CHeat to rise to possible record-
OL,4,Cbreaking highs over rest of bank
OL,5,Choliday weekend
OL,7,FThe less severe alert means
OL,8,Fsignificant impacts on health and
OL,9,Fsocial care services are possible.
